<br>
<br>
as for ease of solo. yes, mages can solo well. not nearly as well as necros, or as fast as wizzies and druids.  we have to know where to hunt to solo effectively. there are some places where wizzies and druids solo that we can't, and certainly more places where necros solo that we can't.  most mages find  a solo spawn taht is easily solo pullable and has a fast spawn time, 6 mins or so. and just sit in that one spot and grind out a lvl.  VERY BORING. yet, pretty fast.  i make great xp solo, provided i'm hunting in the right places. but do you have any clue how boring it is to be the ONLY person in your whole zone?  also, zones where a mage can solo pre epic aren't that common really. in fact, now, many of our favorite solo spots are taken over by uber lvl 60 mellees.. why? mobs we solo tend to have low hp, and not hit too hard.  and the downtime gives them time to BP heal up or regen or bandage. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1844.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=1844.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=1844.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=1844.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1844.topic&index=43><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=1844.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 a